suniya jahnavi-devi lajjita antara
уо ''sau niranjano devas cit-svarupi janardanah sa eva drava-ruреnа gangambho natra samsayah
ananda-nirjharamayim aravinda-nabha-
padaravinda-makarandamaya-pravaham
tam krsna-bhaktim iva murtimatim sravantim
vande mahesvara-siro-ruha-kunda-malam
arudha hara-murdhanam yat-pada-sparsa-gauravat
trailokyam capunad ganga kim tasya mahimocyate
tatheti rajnabhihitam sarva-loka-hitah sivah
dadharavahito gangam pada-puta-jalam hareh
sannivesya mano yasmin chraddhaya munayo ''malah traigunyam dustyajam hitva sadyo yatas tad-atmatam
sarvam krte yuge punyam tretayam puskarah smrtam dvapare tu kuruksetram ganga kali-yuge smrta
yasyamalam divi yasah prathitam rasayam
tatah sapta rsayas tat prabhavabhijna yam nanu tapasa
atyantiki siddhir etavati bhagavati sarvatmani vasudeve
dhatuh kamandalu-jalam tad urukramasya padavanejana-pavitrataya narendra
svardhuny abhun nabhasi sa patati nimarsti loka-trayam bhagavato visadeva kirtih
yaj-jala-sparsa-matrena brahma-danda-hata api sagaratmaja divam jagmuh kevalam deha-bhasmabhih
bhasmibhutanga-sangena svar yatah sagaratmajah kim punah sraddhaya devim sevante ye dhrta-vratah
na hy etat раrат ascaryam svardhunya уad ihoditam ananta-caranambhoja- prasutaya bhava-cchidah
tvat-tire taru-kotarantar-gato gange vihango varam
tvan-nire narakanta-karini varam matsyo ''tha va kacchapah
abhinava-visa-valli pada-padmasya visnor
madana-mathana-mauler malati-puspa-mala jayati jaya-pataka kару asau moksa-laksma
ksapita-kali-kalanka jahnavi nah punatu
yat tat tala-tamala-sala-sarala-vyalola-valli-lata-
snanaya prati-vasaram bhavatu me gangam jalam nirmalam
gangam vari mano-hari murari-carana-cyutam
tripurari-siras-cari papa-hari punatu mam
papapahari duritari taranga-dhari dura-pracari giriraja-guha-vidari
jhankara-kari hari-pada-rajo-vihari gangam punatu satatam subha-kari vari
varam iha nire kamatho minah kim va tire saratah ksinah
atha va gavyutau sva-paco dinas tava dure na nrpati-kulinah',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.1.122','cb','cb.antya.1','ЧБ Антья 1.122',122,NULL,'ye prabhura pada-padme vasati gangara
